B组：Secret vs beastcoast
C组：iG vs Alliance
D组：NaVi vs Liquid
1月19日23点30：小组赛败者组首轮BO3
A组：TNC vs Aster
B组：VG vs Chaos
C组：Reality Rift vs VP
D组：EG vs paiN
